{"id":"east-children-of-the","term":"East, Children of the","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>The Arabs as a whole, known as the Nabateans or Kedarenes, nomad tribes (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Judges 6:3\">Judg. 6:3</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 2:2\">33</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 7:12\">7:12</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 8:10\">8:10</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Judges 6:3","Genesis 2:2","Genesis 7:12","Genesis 8:10"]}